    "id": "cover",
    "label": "Cover",
    "html": "<div class=\"slide slide-title\" style=\"justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-primary);margin-bottom:16px\">PRODUCT LAUNCH 2026</div>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:48px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:20px\">Reimagine What's<br>Possible</h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size:20px;color:var(--color-muted);max-width:600px\">A new approach to building products that people love</p>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "id": "content",
    "label": "Content",
    "html": "<div class=\"slide\" style=\"padding:var(--slide-padding);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px\">Key Advantages</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-bottom:32px\">What sets us apart from the competition</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px\">\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\">\n      <div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--color-primary);opacity:0.15;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center\"><div style=\"width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-primary)\"></div></div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Lightning Fast</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.6\">Sub-millisecond response times with our edge-first architecture</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\">\n      <div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--color-accent,var(--color-primary));opacity:0.15;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center\"><div style=\"width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-accent,var(--color-primary))\"></div></div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Enterprise Ready</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.6\">SOC 2, HIPAA, and GDPR compliant out of the box</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\">\n      <div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--color-secondary,var(--color-primary));opacity:0.15;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center\"><div style=\"width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-secondary,var(--color-primary))\"></div></div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Open Platform</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.6\">Extensible APIs and 200+ integrations in our marketplace</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "id": "data",
    "label": "Metrics",
    "html": "<div class=\"slide\" style=\"padding:var(--slide-padding);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:32px\">By the Numbers</h2>\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-primary);line-height:1\">4.2M</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-top:8px\">Active Users</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-accent,var(--color-primary));line-height:1\">99.9%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-top:8px\">Uptime SLA</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-secondary,var(--color-primary));line-height:1\">3.2x</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-top:8px\">ROI Average</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-primary);line-height:1\">52</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-top:8px\">Countries</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:40px;padding:24px;background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:12px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:12px\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600\">Revenue Growth</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-primary);font-weight:600\">+147%</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"height:8px;background:var(--color-border);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden\">\n      <div style=\"width:72%;height:100%;background:var(--color-primary);border-radius:99px\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div